{"tid":138957,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(又死2件)  父商場抱抱吓失手 兩兄妹4樓墮地慘死","createTime":"2017-03-01T04:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T10:18:51.000Z","uid":78900,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3092815a142440e108a46f6751bb144152ec6e0b","tid":138957,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170301/19943898?_ga=1.93658142.209062677.1478310467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170301%2F19943898%3F_ga%3D1.93658142.209062677.1478310467&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=197d9509\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170301%2F19943898%3F_ga%3D1.93658142.209062677.1478310467&h=95057c76\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170301/19943898?_ga=1.93658142.209062677.1478310467</a><br />\n<br />\n天津有商場發生致命慘劇，一對分別5歲及2歲的小兄妹前晚從商場4樓直墮地庫一樓身亡，有目擊者指當時小兄妹由父親抱住，由於沒抱好，其中一名小孩掉下去，爸爸想拉住小孩時，卻失手令另一個小孩墜樓，一對父母事後在血迹斑斑的地庫一樓，坐在兒女遺體旁嚎哭，令人心酸。<br />\n<br />\n有網民拍到影片，天津南開大悅城地庫一樓的地上躺著兩個小孩，旁邊一對男女軟攤地上痛哭。有目擊者指事發地點在商場4樓，爸爸抱住兩名小孩站在玻璃圍欄旁邊，探頭往下看時，「其中一個孩子沒站穩，掉下去了，大人想把孩子抓住，沒想到另外一個孩子也掉下去了，都沒抓住」，結果眼看一對兒女雙雙墜落地庫一樓，當場慘死。有附近店員表示當時突然聽到一聲巨響，之後地上便躺了兩個小孩。當地警方昨天凌晨確認事件，但具體原因有待進一步調查。據知，小兄妹墜樓的圍欄約1.3米高，旁邊貼有「禁止攀爬」的標誌，在正常情況下，小孩站著也不會越過圍欄墮樓，不過也有網民認為商場應安裝安全防護網，一旦有人墮樓亦可以有緩衝，避免傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6673b715c96f2246a6f25995607bee3e2d20985","tid":138957,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84faf5f517a671987dafa3d277f8c8d545959516","tid":138957,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1975dc6d39b4edbd5559261f3c1349215ada04","tid":138957,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e9e5706118f2afbb4011be91a10981eeaeeefa","tid":138957,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:56:55.000Z","msg":"有內情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驗下dna可能有發現"},{"pid":"7c564cb871a03ba6bc9ba76c08581f03eb5f52f3","tid":138957,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"點解爸爸唔一齊跌埋落去陪佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8eac49710e78cac1668831405f286f72c8be28d","tid":138957,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9416a2e4d7b163289511f995af1004358ba5dc78","tid":138957,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:11:28.000Z","msg":"又可以屈商場賠幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780bb3aadf5433c81c2a47fa53046d8ba27d58da","tid":138957,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解爸爸唔一齊跌埋落去陪佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.